lead_paragraph: Second-seeded Grigor Dimitrov of Bulgaria faces unseeded Diego Schwartzman of Argentina in the final of the Istanbul Open with the two players meeting for the first time.

headline.print_headline: Dimitrov, Schwartzman to Play Istanbul Open Final
